abstract_str: vera kowalski has travelled to __coober__ __pedy__ in search for her son . dane kowalski , 27 , left his diamond creek home in victoria on december 12 for a fishing trip in darwin . his mother said the family are in a living hell at the moment . there has been no trace of him since then , with his phone and bank accounts remaining untouched . three months later his ute has been found on a remote highway . according to family , it appears car became bogged and was abandoned . the disappearance was ` out of character ' and his family and friends have vowed to never give up until he is home .
